<h1>Principles</h1>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Keep it slocial</strong> — Take your time, quality over quantity</li>
  <li><strong>Privacy first</strong> — We don't want your data, just your ideas</li>
  <li><strong>Evergreen only</strong> — Not a place to get your news. Write what matters in a month, a year</li>
  <li><strong>Think generations</strong> — Leave a letter for your great great grandchildren</li>
  <li><strong>Be human</strong> — Thoughtful or funny, both welcome. Just be real</li>
  <li><strong>Patience</strong> — Good thoughts need time to steep</li>
  <li><strong>Clarity</strong> — Say what you mean, mean what you say</li>
  <li><strong>Kindness</strong> — Resonate with others, not against them</li>
  <li><strong>Seek truth together</strong> — Dialectic over debate. We're not here to win, but to understand</li>
  <li><strong>Intention</strong> — One letter a day keeps the noise away</li>
  <li><strong>Simplicity</strong> — No algorithms, no metrics, just words</li>
</ul>
